<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>JP Campbell — Built for the Kingdom</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:#050505;color:#f0ece3;font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;overflow-x:hidden;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;}

:root{
–g:#c8920e;–g2:#dca82a;–gh:#f5d060;–gp:#fae9a0;
–gd:rgba(200,146,14,.08);–gm:rgba(200,146,14,.22);–gg:rgba(200,146,14,.35);
–t:#00c4b4;–th:#00e8d6;–td:rgba(0,196,180,.08);–tm:rgba(0,196,180,.22);
–black:#050505;–panel:#0d0d0d;
–border:rgba(255,255,255,.06);–border-hi:rgba(255,255,255,.1);
–w:#f0ece3;–c:#c8c4ba;–mu:#5a5a54;–mh:#909088;
}

.noise{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;background-image:url(“data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=‘0 0 200 200’ xmlns=‘http://www.w3.org/2000/svg’%3E%3Cfilter id=‘n’%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=‘fractalNoise’ baseFrequency=’.85’ numOctaves=‘4’/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=‘100%25’ height=‘100%25’ filter=‘url(%23n)’ opacity=’.04’/%3E%3C/svg%3E”);background-size:180px;opacity:.5;}

/* ══ COVER ══ */
.cover{position:relative;z-index:1;min-height:100svh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;overflow:hidden;background:var(–black);}

.cover-grid{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(200,146,14,.06) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(200,146,14,.06) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:44px 44px;transform:perspective(400px) rotateX(28deg) translateY(15%) scale(1.8);transform-origin:50% 100%;animation:gridPull 16s linear infinite;mask-image:linear-gradient(to top,black 0%,transparent 50%);-webkit-mask-image:linear-gradient(to top,black 0%,transparent 50%);}
@keyframes gridPull{from{background-position:0 0;}to{background-position:0 44px;}}

.cover-glow{position:absolute;top:10%;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:min(120vw,700px);height:min(120vw,700px);background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(200,146,14,.15) 0%,rgba(0,196,180,.07) 45%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;animation:breathe 6s ease-in-out infinite;}
@keyframes breathe{0%,100%{opacity:.7;transform:translateX(-50%) scale(1);}50%{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) scale(1.07);}}

.beams{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;overflow:hidden;}
.bm{position:absolute;top:-20%;bottom:-20%;width:1px;transform-origin:top;}
.bm:nth-child(1){left:10%;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,rgba(200,146,14,.2),transparent);transform:rotate(8deg);animation:bmFade 7s 0s ease-in-out infinite;}
.bm:nth-child(2){left:32%;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,rgba(0,196,180,.14),transparent);transform:rotate(4deg);animation:bmFade 9s 2s ease-in-out infinite;}
.bm:nth-child(3){right:28%;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,rgba(200,146,14,.16),transparent);transform:rotate(-6deg);animation:bmFade 8s 4s ease-in-out infinite;}
.bm:nth-child(4){right:8%;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,rgba(0,196,180,.12),transparent);transform:rotate(-12deg);animation:bmFade 6s 1s ease-in-out infinite;}
@keyframes bmFade{0%,100%{opacity:0;}40%,60%{opacity:1;}}

.scan{position:absolute;left:0;right:0;height:1px;pointer-events:none;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(200,146,14,.45) 40%,rgba(0,196,180,.35) 60%,transparent);animation:scanDown 12s linear infinite;top:0;}
@keyframes scanDown{0%{top:-2px;opacity:0;}5%{opacity:1;}95%{opacity:.5;}100%{top:100%;opacity:0;}}

.topbar{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:4px;z-index:3;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–t),var(–g),var(–gh),var(–g),var(–t));background-size:300% 100%;animation:topBar 3s linear infinite;}
@keyframes topBar{0%{background-position:100% 0;}100%{background-position:-200% 0;}}

.cover-top{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:clamp(36px,9vw,64px) clamp(24px,7vw,48px) 0;}
.c-eyebrow{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(9px,2.5vw,11px);letter-spacing:.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–t);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:clamp(28px,7vw,48px);opacity:0;animation:up .8s .1s forwards;}
.c-eyebrow::before{content:’’;width:clamp(18px,5vw,32px);height:1px;background:var(–t);flex-shrink:0;}
.c-eyebrow::after{content:’’;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(–t);box-shadow:0 0 12px var(–t);animation:blink 2s infinite;}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1;}50%{opacity:.1;}}

.c-name{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(76px,21vw,160px);line-height:.88;letter-spacing:.02em;color:var(–w);opacity:0;animation:up 1s .25s forwards;}
.c-name span{display:block;position:relative;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:clamp(1px,.2vw,2px) var(–g);}
.c-name span::after{content:attr(data-t);position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(105deg,var(–g) 0%,var(–gh) 28%,var(–gp) 50%,var(–gh) 72%,var(–g) 100%);background-size:400% 100%;-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:0;animation:goldShimmer 5s ease-in-out infinite;}
@keyframes goldShimmer{0%,100%{background-position:0%;}50%{background-position:100%;}}

.c-title{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(10px,2.8vw,13px);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–g2);margin-top:clamp(8px,2.5vw,14px);opacity:0;animation:up .8s .5s forwards;}

.cover-mid{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:clamp(28px,7vw,48px) clamp(24px,7vw,48px);opacity:0;animation:up .8s .7s forwards;}
.c-scr-ref{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(9px,2.5vw,11px);letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–t);margin-bottom:clamp(10px,3vw,16px);}
.c-scr-verse{font-size:clamp(21px,5.8vw,32px);font-style:italic;font-weight:400;color:var(–gh);line-height:1.5;border-left:3px solid var(–g);padding-left:clamp(16px,4vw,24px);}

.cover-bot{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:0 clamp(24px,7vw,48px) clamp(40px,9vw,64px);opacity:0;animation:up .8s .9s forwards;}
.c-mission-lbl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(8px,2.2vw,10px);letter-spacing:.24em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–mh);margin-bottom:clamp(8px,2.5vw,12px);}
.c-mission{font-size:clamp(20px,5.5vw,30px);font-weight:700;color:var(–w);line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:clamp(20px,5vw,28px);}
.c-mission em{color:var(–th);font-style:normal;}

@keyframes up{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

/* ══ SECTIONS ══ */
.sec{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:clamp(56px,13vw,96px) clamp(24px,7vw,48px);border-top:1px solid var(–border);overflow:hidden;}
.sec-lbl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(9px,2.5vw,11px);letter-spacing:.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–t);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:clamp(6px,2vw,10px);}
.sec-lbl::before{content:’’;width:clamp(16px,4vw,28px);height:1px;background:var(–t);flex-shrink:0;}
.sec-title{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(44px,12vw,80px);letter-spacing:.03em;line-height:.9;color:var(–w);margin-bottom:clamp(28px,7vw,44px);}

/* Scripture */
.scripture{padding:clamp(18px,5vw,26px) clamp(18px,5vw,26px) clamp(18px,5vw,26px) clamp(22px,6vw,32px);border:1px solid var(–gm);background:rgba(200,146,14,.05);margin-bottom:clamp(24px,6vw,36px);position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.scripture::before{content:’\201C’;position:absolute;top:-8px;left:10px;font-size:clamp(56px,15vw,88px);color:var(–g);opacity:.18;font-family:Georgia,serif;line-height:1;pointer-events:none;}
.scr-ref{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(8px,2.2vw,10px);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–g);margin-bottom:clamp(6px,2vw,10px);}
.scr-verse{font-size:clamp(18px,4.8vw,24px);font-style:italic;font-weight:400;color:var(–gh);line-height:1.6;}

/* Body */
.body{font-size:clamp(17px,4.5vw,22px);font-weight:400;color:var(–c);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:clamp(20px,5vw,32px);}
.body strong{color:var(–w);font-weight:700;}

/* ══ THE PROGRAM — big letter pillars ══ */
.pillar{padding:clamp(22px,6vw,32px) clamp(20px,5.5vw,28px);border:1px solid var(–border);background:rgba(0,0,0,.5);position:relative;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:3px;}
.pillar::after{content:’’;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(–pc,var(–g));}
.pillar-letter{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(64px,17vw,96px);line-height:1;color:var(–pc,var(–g));margin-bottom:clamp(4px,1.5vw,8px);}
.pillar-name{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,7.5vw,44px);letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(–w);line-height:1;margin-bottom:clamp(10px,3vw,14px);}
.pillar-body{font-size:clamp(16px,4.3vw,20px);font-weight:400;color:var(–c);line-height:1.7;}

/* ══ THE TOOLS — cards ══ */
.tool-card{padding:clamp(20px,5.5vw,28px);border:1px solid var(–border);background:rgba(0,0,0,.45);position:relative;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:3px;display:flex;gap:clamp(14px,4vw,20px);align-items:flex-start;}
.tool-card::before{content:’’;position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:3px;background:var(–tc,var(–t));}
.tool-icon{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(32px,9vw,48px);line-height:1;color:var(–tc,var(–t));flex-shrink:0;min-width:clamp(32px,9vw,48px);}
.tool-body{}
.tool-name{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,6vw,34px);letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(–w);line-height:1;margin-bottom:clamp(6px,2vw,10px);}
.tool-desc{font-size:clamp(15px,4vw,18px);font-weight:400;color:var(–c);line-height:1.65;}

/* ══ THE TRANSFORMATION ══ */
.transform-intro{
font-size:clamp(26px,7vw,40px);
font-weight:700;font-style:italic;
color:var(–w);line-height:1.35;
margin-bottom:clamp(24px,6vw,36px);
}
.transform-intro em{color:var(–th);font-style:normal;}

.t-card{padding:clamp(22px,6vw,32px) clamp(20px,5.5vw,28px);border:1px solid var(–border);background:rgba(0,0,0,.45);position:relative;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:3px;}
.t-card::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(–tc,var(–t));}
.t-num{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(11px,3vw,14px);letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(–tc,var(–t));margin-bottom:clamp(6px,2vw,8px);}
.t-title{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,7vw,40px);letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(–w);line-height:1;margin-bottom:clamp(8px,2.5vw,12px);}
.t-body{font-size:clamp(15px,4vw,18px);font-weight:400;color:var(–c);line-height:1.65;}

/* 5th card — red hit */
.t-card-red{border-color:rgba(224,85,85,.25);background:rgba(224,85,85,.04);}
.t-card-red::before{background:#e05555;}
.t-card-red .t-num{color:#e05555;}
.t-card-red .t-title{color:var(–w);}

/* ══ CLOSING ══ */
.closing{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:clamp(64px,14vw,100px) clamp(24px,7vw,48px);border-top:1px solid var(–border);text-align:center;overflow:hidden;}
.closing::before{content:’’;position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%,rgba(0,196,180,.09) 0%,rgba(200,146,14,.07) 50%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;animation:breathe 8s ease-in-out infinite;}
.closing-inner{position:relative;z-index:1;}

/* Giant closing X watermark */
.closing-wm{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:min(80vw,480px);line-height:1;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(200,146,14,.06);pointer-events:none;user-select:none;animation:breathe 10s ease-in-out infinite;}

.closing-name{font-family:‘Bebas Neue’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(52px,14vw,88px);letter-spacing:.03em;line-height:.9;color:var(–w);margin-bottom:clamp(8px,2.5vw,12px);}
.closing-name em{display:block;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px var(–g);}
.closing-title{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(9px,2.5vw,12px);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–t);margin-bottom:clamp(32px,8vw,52px);}

.closing-scripture{padding:clamp(20px,5.5vw,28px);border:1px solid var(–gm);background:rgba(200,146,14,.05);max-width:min(480px,90vw);margin:0 auto clamp(24px,6vw,36px);}
.cls-verse{font-size:clamp(18px,5vw,24px);font-style:italic;font-weight:400;color:var(–gh);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:clamp(8px,2.5vw,12px);}
.cls-ref{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(8px,2.2vw,10px);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–g);}

.closing-rule{width:56px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(–t),var(–g),transparent);margin:0 auto;}

footer{position:relative;z-index:1;background:rgba(0,0,0,.8);border-top:1px solid var(–border);padding:clamp(16px,4vw,22px) clamp(24px,7vw,48px);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;}
.fl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(8px,2vw,10px);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–mu);}
.fr{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:clamp(8px,2vw,10px);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–t);}

.rv{opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);transition:opacity .9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1),transform .9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);}
.rv.in{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="noise"></div>

<!-- ══ COVER ══ -->

<section class="cover">
  <div class="cover-grid"></div>
  <div class="cover-glow"></div>
  <div class="beams"><div class="bm"></div><div class="bm"></div><div class="bm"></div><div class="bm"></div></div>
  <div class="scan"></div>
  <div class="topbar"></div>

  <div class="cover-top">
    <div class="c-eyebrow">Built for the Kingdom</div>
    <div class="c-name">JP<br><span data-t="Campbell">Campbell</span></div>
    <div class="c-title">Business Coach &nbsp;·&nbsp; Sales Operator</div>
  </div>

  <div class="cover-mid">
    <div class="c-scr-ref">Ephesians 2:10</div>
    <div class="c-scr-verse">"For we are God's handiwork, created in Christ Jesus to do good works, which God prepared in advance for us to do."</div>
  </div>

  <div class="cover-bot">
    <div class="c-mission-lbl">The mission</div>
    <div class="c-mission">Teaching <em>Kingdom entrepreneurs</em> to build real businesses — without compromising who they are.</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ THE PROGRAM ══ -->

<section class="sec rv" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 20%,rgba(200,146,14,.09) 0%,transparent 55%) #050505;">
  <div class="sec-lbl">The program</div>
  <div class="sec-title">What MSO is.</div>

  <div class="scripture">
    <div class="scr-ref">Proverbs 24:3–4</div>
    <div class="scr-verse">"By wisdom a house is built, and through understanding it is established; through knowledge its rooms are filled with rare and beautiful treasures."</div>
  </div>

  <div class="body">MSO stands for <strong>Marketing, Sales, and Operations.</strong> It also stands for <strong>Manufacturer's Special Order</strong> — because this isn't a generic course. It's a custom-engineered system built to the Manufacturer's specifications for that person's business and calling.</div>
  <div class="body">Three parts. Built in order. Because you can't close what you haven't attracted, and you can't scale what you haven't built.</div>

  <div class="pillar" style="--pc:var(--t)">
    <div class="pillar-letter">M</div>
    <div class="pillar-name">Marketing</div>
    <div class="pillar-body">Getting the right people in front of you. Who you serve, what you offer, how you show up on Instagram — and how you start real conversations that go somewhere.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="pillar" style="--pc:var(--g)">
    <div class="pillar-letter">S</div>
    <div class="pillar-name">Sales</div>
    <div class="pillar-body">Not pressure. Not manipulation. A service-first process where you ask the right questions, find the real need, and offer a real solution. The close is a side effect of doing it right.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="pillar" style="--pc:var(--t)">
    <div class="pillar-letter">O</div>
    <div class="pillar-name">Operations</div>
    <div class="pillar-body">Building the backend machine — fulfillment, systems, tracking — so the business runs with consistency and you stop being the bottleneck in your own calling.</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ THE TOOLS ══ -->

<section class="sec rv" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 70%,rgba(0,196,180,.08) 0%,transparent 55%) #080808;">
  <div class="sec-lbl">The tools</div>
  <div class="sec-title">What's in the system.</div>

  <div class="scripture">
    <div class="scr-ref">Habakkuk 2:2</div>
    <div class="scr-verse">"Write the vision and make it plain on tablets, that he may run who reads it."</div>
  </div>

  <div class="body">Every Builder walks away with real tools — not concepts, not theory. Things they can hold, use, and hand off.</div>

  <div class="tool-card" style="--tc:var(--t)">
    <div class="tool-icon">01</div>
    <div class="tool-body">
      <div class="tool-name">The Blueprint</div>
      <div class="tool-desc">The full curriculum — their personal roadmap through all five build phases, documented and ready to follow.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-card" style="--tc:var(--g)">
    <div class="tool-icon">02</div>
    <div class="tool-body">
      <div class="tool-name">The Pathway</div>
      <div class="tool-desc">A built and live Instagram DM funnel — from first contact to booked appointment, automated and running.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-card" style="--tc:var(--t)">
    <div class="tool-icon">03</div>
    <div class="tool-body">
      <div class="tool-name">The POWER Framework</div>
      <div class="tool-desc">A full sales script for The Consult — written, rehearsed, and internalized. Every objection mapped. Every close trained.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-card" style="--tc:var(--g)">
    <div class="tool-icon">04</div>
    <div class="tool-body">
      <div class="tool-name">The Gauges</div>
      <div class="tool-desc">A live tracking dashboard — ad spend, messages, Consults, closes, cash. Decisions come from data, not gut feelings.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-card" style="--tc:var(--t)">
    <div class="tool-icon">05</div>
    <div class="tool-body">
      <div class="tool-name">The Gatekeeper SOP</div>
      <div class="tool-desc">A documented setter system — so someone else can qualify Candidates and protect the Pathway on their behalf.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tool-card" style="--tc:var(--g)">
    <div class="tool-icon">06</div>
    <div class="tool-body">
      <div class="tool-name">The Receipt</div>
      <div class="tool-desc">A real case study — documented proof that the system works. The first win that fuels every conversation after it.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ THE TRANSFORMATION ══ -->

<section class="sec rv" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 75% 30%,rgba(200,146,14,.08) 0%,transparent 55%) #050505;">
  <div class="sec-lbl">The transformation</div>
  <div class="sec-title">What changes.</div>

  <div class="scripture">
    <div class="scr-ref">Proverbs 22:29</div>
    <div class="scr-verse">"Do you see someone skilled in their work? They will serve before kings; they will not serve before officials of low rank."</div>
  </div>

  <div class="transform-intro">This isn't about<br><em>hustle harder.</em><br>It's about build smarter.</div>

  <div class="t-card" style="--tc:var(--t)">
    <div class="t-num">Before → After</div>
    <div class="t-title">Guessing → Data</div>
    <div class="t-body">They stop making decisions based on feelings and start reading real numbers every morning. The Gauges eliminate the guesswork.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="t-card" style="--tc:var(--g)">
    <div class="t-num">Before → After</div>
    <div class="t-title">Chasing → Qualifying</div>
    <div class="t-body">They stop chasing anyone who looks like a prospect and start attracting real Candidates — people who already want what they offer.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="t-card" style="--tc:var(--t)">
    <div class="t-num">Before → After</div>
    <div class="t-title">Pitching → Serving</div>
    <div class="t-body">The Consult isn't a sales call. It's a diagnostic. They ask the right questions, find the real need, and serve — the close follows naturally.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="t-card" style="--tc:var(--g)">
